&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen at the Royal Cornwall Hospital on Gwithian Unit. Gwithian is a busy outpatient area with 4 day beds for children and young people. This role will involve assisting in clinics and undertaking procedures such as venepuncture once training is completed. Are you a flexible, adaptable individual who enjoys one day being different from another? Are you able to work as part of the team?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a part time post: 23 hours per week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sarah Morrison, Lead Nurse: 01872 253004&lt;/p&gt;
